# Komet Pipeline Workspace .gitignore
# ════════════════════════════════════
#
# Ignore everything, whitelist only workspace-owned files.
# Component repos are independent git repos cloned by ike:init.

# ── Ignore everything by default ─────────────────────────────────
*

# ── Whitelist workspace-level files ──────────────────────────────
!.gitignore
!pom.xml
!workspace.yaml
!README.adoc
!SPLIT-BRAIN.adoc

# ── Whitelist workspace-owned directories ────────────────────────
!.mvn/
!.mvn/**
!checkpoints/
!checkpoints/**
!.run/
!.run/**
